(188, 1, '2018-09-13 21:04:10', '2018-09-13 18:04:10', '<p class=\"a-spacing-base\"><span class=\"a-text-bold\">Heavy Bass Driven Sound</span>and Stylish Earphones by Betron  these in-ear headphones from Betron are easy to slip into a pocket or backpack. Their punchy bass driven audio output unlocks more detail in every track and with a handy built-in microphone, taking and making calls is simple.<!--more--></p>\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\">Noise Isolation Technology</p>\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/wordpress/index.php/2018/09/13/betron-ysm1000-headphones-earbuds-high-definition-in-ear-noise-isolating-heavy-deep-bass-for-iphone-ipod-ipad-mp3-players-samsung-galaxy-nokia-htc-etc-gold-without-mic/earphone-review-1/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-172\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-172 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/earphone-review-1-100x100.jpg\" alt=\"Noise Isolation Technology\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>These earphones have flawless noise isolation technology, which allows you to be fully immersed with the acoustics. Complete with a strong heavy bass, these key features provide personalized and high quality listening; giving you the ultimate audio experience.\n\n&nbsp;\n<h4></h4>\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Gold plated 3.5mm connector</h4>\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/wordpress/index.php/2018/09/13/betron-ysm1000-headphones-earbuds-high-definition-in-ear-noise-isolating-heavy-deep-bass-for-iphone-ipod-ipad-mp3-players-samsung-galaxy-nokia-htc-etc-gold-without-mic/earphone-reviee-2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-173\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-173\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/earphone-reviee-2-100x100.jpg\" alt=\"Gold plated 3.5mm connector\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>Gold is highly resistant to corrosion or oxidation, so prevents poor connections from those sources.It is also fairly soft, so the mating surfaces deform slightly, increasing contact area to reduce resistance. The gold plating is very thin, so the added resistance from the gold is easily overcome by its other properties.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Tangle Free Cable</h4>\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/wordpress/index.php/2018/09/13/betron-ysm1000-headphones-earbuds-high-definition-in-ear-noise-isolating-heavy-deep-bass-for-iphone-ipod-ipad-mp3-players-samsung-galaxy-nokia-htc-etc-gold-without-mic/earphone-review-3/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-175\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-175\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/earphone-review-3-100x100.jpg\" alt=\"Tangle Free Cable\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>When using some wired earbuds, one of the annoying problems you face is the tangling of the wires. That\'s where tangle-free earbuds come into play.Click this<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Betron-YSM1000-Headphones-Definition-Isolating/dp/B00S2P0M1C/ref=sr_1_2_sspa?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1536860199&amp;sr=8-2-spons&amp;keywords=earphones&amp;psc=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> link</a> to order your own.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;', 'Betron YSM1000 Headphones, Earbuds, High Definition, in-Ear, Noise Isolating, Heavy Deep Bass for iPhone, iPod, iPad, MP3 Players, Samsung Galaxy, Nokia, HTC, etc (Gold Without Mic)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '169-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-09-13 21:04:10', '2018-09-13 18:04:10', '', 169, 'http://localhost:8080/wordpress/index.php/2018/09/13/169-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
